<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 02:15:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>费城剧院因担心亲巴勒斯坦人的强烈反对而取消放映以色列电影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/philadelphia-theater-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-over-fear-of-pro-palestinian-backlash/0000018e-bfdc-db65-a7af-ffdcb9a70000</link><description>布林莫尔电影学院原定在费城举行的年度以色列电影节上放映一部关于以色列音乐家耶胡达·波利克 (Yehuda Poliker) 的纪录片，但在提前一天通知后就取消了该学院</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 22:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/philadelphia-theater-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-over-fear-of-pro-palestinian-backlash/0000018e-bfdc-db65-a7af-ffdcb9a70000</guid></item><item><title>参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦：以色列在加沙的行动可能在法律上构成种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/sen-elizabeth-warren-israels-actions-in-gaza-may-legally-constitute-genocide/0000018e-bf87-d6f4-afaf-bfc7919d0000</link><description>尽管几位批评以色列的进步派众议院议员表示，他们个人认为这次军事行动构成了种族灭绝，但没有人敢直截了当地这么说。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 21:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/sen-elizabeth-warren-israels-actions-in-gaza-may-legally-constitute-genocide/0000018e-bf87-d6f4-afaf-bfc7919d0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔：最新提案将弥合人质谈判中的分歧；哈马斯否认进展报告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/qatar-latest-proposal-bridges-gaps-in-hostage-talks-hamas-denies-reports-of-progress/0000018e-bf65-d480-a99e-ff77153b0000</link><description>调解员等待以色列和哈马斯的回应；以色列消息人士称，协议要求哈马斯提供第一阶段释放的 40 名人质的姓名，并保证他们还活着，以换取原则上同意允许巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部的家园</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 20:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/qatar-latest-proposal-bridges-gaps-in-hostage-talks-hamas-denies-reports-of-progress/0000018e-bf65-d480-a99e-ff77153b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判的关键证人拿执法部门开玩笑。现在他正在付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial-made-a-joke-of-law-enforcement-now-hes-paying-the-price/0000018e-bf19-d6f4-afaf-bf5b478e0000</link><description>什洛莫·菲尔伯在代表国家作证之前就明确表明了他的忠诚所在。在检察官宣布计划取消与他的协议后，下一步就是对他提出指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 20:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial-made-a-joke-of-law-enforcement-now-hes-paying-the-price/0000018e-bf19-d6f4-afaf-bf5b478e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列迷失了方向，内塔尼亚胡不知道他要把我们带到哪里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-is-lost-and-netanyahu-has-no-idea-where-hes-taking-us/0000018e-be71-d480-a99e-fe77a9cf0000</link><description>当我的导航应用程序被以色列军队的 GPS 干扰器弄得毫无用处时，我突然意识到，我在路上感受到的不安全和不确定感与 10 月 7 日以来的全国情绪完全一致</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 18:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-is-lost-and-netanyahu-has-no-idea-where-hes-taking-us/0000018e-be71-d480-a99e-fe77a9cf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家检察官表示将撤销在内塔尼亚胡审判中与关键证人达成的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-attorney-says-it-will-revoke-agreement-with-key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial/0000018e-becd-d480-a99e-fedfb5c00000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的心腹、政府 4000 号案件的关键证人什洛莫·菲尔伯 (Shlomo Filber) 在出庭作证时未能遵守协议条款。在作证期间，菲尔伯撤回了他之前提出的几项主张，导致检察官要求法庭宣布他为敌对证人</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 18:07:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-attorney-says-it-will-revoke-agreement-with-key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial/0000018e-becd-d480-a99e-fedfb5c00000</guid></item><item><title>“他们无缘无故朝我肚子开枪”：以色列青少年讲述在加沙被囚禁的经历</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/they-shot-me-in-the-stomach-for-no-reason-israeli-teen-recounts-captivity-in-gaza/0000018e-be4f-d8c8-afbe-feffb99e0000</link><description>11 月获释的利亚姆·奥尔 (Liam Or) 表示，直到获释那天他才知道 10 月 7 日发生了什么，而且他和在新星节上被劫持的人质奥马尔 (Omer) 相信他们是唯一的以色列人质</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 17:39:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/they-shot-me-in-the-stomach-for-no-reason-israeli-teen-recounts-captivity-in-gaza/0000018e-be4f-d8c8-afbe-feffb99e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 185 天：白宫称向哈马斯提出新的休战提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-185-new-truce-proposal-presented-to-hamas-white-house-says/0000018e-be79-d480-a99e-fe7fc2490001</link><description>外国外交官对协议表示“谨慎乐观”；哈马斯否认取得进展 ■ 本格维尔：如果内塔尼亚胡在没有拉法行动的情况下结束战争，内塔尼亚胡将失去总理职位 ■ 外国记者协会呼吁以色列“不受限制地进入加沙” ■ 以色列国防军：士兵射杀了试图刺伤的巴勒斯坦妇女他们在约旦河西岸检查站 ■ 伊朗外长表示“未来的日子对以色列来说将是艰难的” ■ 战争开始 185 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 16:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-185-new-truce-proposal-presented-to-hamas-white-house-says/0000018e-be79-d480-a99e-fe7fc2490001</guid></item><item><title>迈达斯王逆转：本杰明·内塔尼亚胡、加沙战争和价值毁灭的艺术</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/king-midas-in-reverse-benjamin-netanyahu-the-gaza-war-and-the-art-of-value-destruction/0000018e-bdb4-de0c-a3cf-fff668dd0000</link><description>在外交上，10月7日之后，以色列在加沙对抗哈马斯的战争中一切顺利。然后内塔尼亚胡的傲慢、管理不善和不诚实的无能接管了一切</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 16:10:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/king-midas-in-reverse-benjamin-netanyahu-the-gaza-war-and-the-art-of-value-destruction/0000018e-bdb4-de0c-a3cf-fff668dd0000</guid></item><item><title>外国记者协会呼吁以色列取消对加沙独立媒体的禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/foreign-press-association-calls-on-israel-to-lift-ban-on-independent-press-in-gaza/0000018e-be21-d92b-adaf-fe6513ea0000</link><description>FPA董事会表示，是否前往加沙实地的决定应由每个国际媒体自行决定，全面禁令限制了世界目睹战争给各方带来的真正代价的能力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:18:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/foreign-press-association-calls-on-israel-to-lift-ban-on-independent-press-in-gaza/0000018e-be21-d92b-adaf-fe6513ea0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日加沙战争六周年纪念日，全球各地举行集会和抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/rallies-protests-held-across-the-globe-on-six-month-anniversary-of-oct-7-war-in-gaza/0000018e-bdcb-db65-a7af-fdcba4940000</link><description>周日，前人质、人质家属和领导人向挤满的人群发表讲话，这是 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以色列已有半年的日子</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:03:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/rallies-protests-held-across-the-globe-on-six-month-anniversary-of-oct-7-war-in-gaza/0000018e-bdcb-db65-a7af-fdcba4940000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔任命新警察局长，因滥用职权和违反信任而受到调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-picks-new-police-chief-who-was-investigated-for-abusing-powers-breach-of-trust/0000018e-be20-d6f4-afaf-be62f23a0000</link><description>2015年，时任警察局长阿尔谢奇拒绝了内部调查部门拒绝阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德晋升的建议。警方消息人士称佩莱德为“本-格维尔的傀儡”，两人的关系可以追溯到十多年前</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 14:44:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-picks-new-police-chief-who-was-investigated-for-abusing-powers-breach-of-trust/0000018e-be20-d6f4-afaf-be62f23a0000</guid></item><item><title>备受争议的影响力活动背后的官员被任命为内塔尼亚胡的军事部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-new-military-secretary-is-an-officer-who-used-a-minor-for-unauthorized-psy-ops/0000018e-bde4-d753-a7ee-ffe7657c0000</link><description>双桅船。总理任命的罗曼·戈夫曼 (Roman Gofman) 将军批准向一名 17 岁的年轻人发送机密材料，要求他在网上发布这些材料。该少年随后被指控从事间谍活动，并被关押了 18 个月，直到以色列国防军称他为军事情报部门工作并将他释放。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 14:19:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-new-military-secretary-is-an-officer-who-used-a-minor-for-unauthorized-psy-ops/0000018e-bde4-d753-a7ee-ffe7657c0000</guid></item><item><title>被指控在特拉维夫碾压抗议者的司机将被释放并软禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/driver-accused-of-running-over-protesters-in-tel-aviv-to-be-released-to-house-arrest/0000018e-bdbc-d871-ad9e-fffe33850000</link><description>法院表示，有合理的理由相信海姆·西洛特金犯下了这一罪行，但可能需要相当长的时间来审查他对事件的说法。警方要求推迟一天释放，以便他们可以就这一决定提出上诉</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 13:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/driver-accused-of-running-over-protesters-in-tel-aviv-to-be-released-to-house-arrest/0000018e-bdbc-d871-ad9e-fffe33850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军消息来源证实真主党首次击落先进的 Hermes 900 无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-in-a-first-hezbollah-shoots-down-advanced-hermes-900-uav/0000018e-bd86-d92b-adaf-ffe63fde0000</link><description>Hermes 900 是一款多用途无人机，飞行时间为 36 小时。它的两架前身 Hermes 450 过去曾遭到袭击，但周六的拦截事件代价高昂，提醒人们以色列国防军无人机并非无懈可击</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 12:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-in-a-first-hezbollah-shoots-down-advanced-hermes-900-uav/0000018e-bd86-d92b-adaf-ffe63fde0000</guid></item><item><title>在所有施压策略都用尽的情况下，以色列和哈马斯现在必须谈判达成真正的加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/all-pressure-tactics-exhausted-israel-and-hamas-must-now-negotiate-a-real-gaza-deal/0000018e-bd08-dfde-a3ef-bf7bbc180000</link><description>如果迄今为止，以色列的政策依赖于调解者的外交努力及其自身的军事力量，那么谈判现在取决于美国政府和以色列公众压力 — — 及其对总理可能构成的政治威胁</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/all-pressure-tactics-exhausted-israel-and-hamas-must-now-negotiate-a-real-gaza-deal/0000018e-bd08-dfde-a3ef-bf7bbc180000</guid></item><item><title>世界法院就指控德国在加沙战争中援助以色列的案件举行听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/world-court-opens-hearings-in-a-case-accusing-germany-of-aiding-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018e-bd28-df12-afaf-bfad44f30000</link><description>尼加拉瓜向国际法院请愿，称通过向以色列提供政治、财政和军事支持以及取消对近东救济工程处的资助，“德国正在为种族灭绝的实施提供便利”，并寻求结束德国对以色列的军事和其他援助</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 10:45:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/world-court-opens-hearings-in-a-case-accusing-germany-of-aiding-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018e-bd28-df12-afaf-bfad44f30000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：随着加沙战争进入六个月大关，内塔尼亚胡失去了议会多数席位；甘茨保持领先</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/polls-netanyahu-loses-knesset-majority-as-gaza-war-hits-six-month-mark-gantz-stays-ahead/0000018e-bd00-dbdb-adaf-bfe55e700000</link><description>两项调查均显示甘茨领导的政党以 32-30 个席位领先，内塔尼亚胡领导的利库德集团以 21-19 个席位紧随其后。两项民意调查均未显示财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇的宗教犹太复国主义跨过选举门槛</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:55:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/polls-netanyahu-loses-knesset-majority-as-gaza-war-hits-six-month-mark-gantz-stays-ahead/0000018e-bd00-dbdb-adaf-bfe55e700000</guid></item><item><title>发表以色列作家共存文章的格尔尼卡编辑辞职，称她不同意撤稿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/guernica-editor-who-published-israeli-writers-coexistence-essay-resigns/0000018e-bce5-df26-a99e-fcff51e00000</link><description>“该杂志坚持撤回该作品； 《格尔尼卡》杂志主编吉娜·摩尔 (Jina Moore) 写道：“我不这么认为。”在《格尔尼卡》撤回英裔以色列作家兼翻译家乔安娜·陈 (Joanna Chen) 的文章一个月后，她宣布辞职。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/guernica-editor-who-published-israeli-writers-coexistence-essay-resigns/0000018e-bce5-df26-a99e-fcff51e00000</guid></item><item><title>亲爱的拜登总统，您同意以色列定居者使用美国武器吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/fyi-joe-biden-israels-settlers-use-american-weapons/0000018e-b82b-d906-a5cf-babfb7800000</link><description>这些武器正被一个与军队类似的恐吓、恐怖和掠夺政权所使用，该政权是由国家公民及其代理人在西岸建立的政权</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/fyi-joe-biden-israels-settlers-use-american-weapons/0000018e-b82b-d906-a5cf-babfb7800000</guid></item></channel></rss>